data.description: Welcome to this charming 1994 brick ranch home, a timeless gem nestled in a welcoming neighborhood. Boasting a one-car garage, three bedrooms, and two full bathrooms, this home offers both comfort and convenience. The cozy interior is enhanced by a wood-burning fireplace in the spacious living area, providing a warm and inviting atmosphere for gatherings or quiet evenings.Enjoy the freedom of no HOA restrictions as you revel in the fully fenced-in backyard, offering privacy and a secure space for outdoor activities or furry friends. This centrally located home places you in close proximity to the Town of Moncks Corner, ensuring easy access to its amenities and attractions. Embrace the convenience of thisprime location, combining the tranquility of a well-established neighborhood with the vibrancy of nearby shops, restaurants, and recreational opportunities. Don't miss the chance to make this home your own!
